N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 42.3 - Labeling and marking of containers

State Regulations

The label and marking on every package, can or container of
brake fluid sold or distributed or kept for sale in this State must conform to
the standard referred to in section
42.1
